text: Bharuch INA is a town and an industrial notified area in Bharuch district in the state of Gujarat, India. ==Demographics== India census, Bharuch INA had a population of 391. Males constitute 56% of the population and females 44%. Bharuch INA has an average literacy rate of 72%, higher than the national average of 59.5%; with male literacy of 76% and female literacy of 66%. 13% of the population is under 6 years of age. ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Bharuch district
